<p>
<b><i>HP NewWave Environment</i></b><br>
Hewlett-Packard Co., Personal Software Division, 3410 Central Expwy,, Santa 
Clara, CA 95051; (800) 752-0900.<br>
<b>List Price:</b> $195<br>
<b>Requires:</b> 4MB EMS 4.0 expanded memory, hard disk, <i>Microsoft Windows/286</i><br>
<b>In Short:</b> By bringing object-oriented concepts to applications and to 
the documents they create, the <i>HP NewWave Environment</i> demonstrates the 
next major advancement in graphical user interfaces,
</p>

